<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="page-shell">
      <section class="hero-card hero-card-home hero-card-projects">
        <%- include("../components/navbar", { active: typeof active !== "undefined" ? active : "projects" }) %>
        <%- include("jumbotron") %>
      </section>

      <main class="content">
        <section class="section-heading" id="project-showcase">
          <h2>PROJECTS</h2>
          <p>
            Projects showcase
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="filters">
          <div class="filter-tabs">
            <button class="tab is-active">All</button>
            <button class="tab">Projects</button>
            <button class="tab">Learnings</button>
            <button class="tab">Careers</button>
          </div>

    
        </section>

        <section class="post-grid">
          <article class="post-card ">
            <div class="post-image image-1">
              <span class="pill">Destination</span>
            </div>
            <div class="project-stack" aria-label="Project tech stack">
              <span>
                <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/go/go-original.svg" alt="Go" />
                Go
              </span>
              <span>
                <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/postgresql/postgresql-original.svg" alt="PostgreSQL" />
                PostgreSQL
              </span>
              <span>
                <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/redis/redis-original.svg" alt="Redis" />
                Redis
              </span>
            </div>
            <div class="post-meta">30 Jan 2024 • 10 mins read</div>
            <h3>Unveiling the Secrets Beyond the Tourist Trails</h3>
            <p>
              Dive into the local culture, discover hidden spots, and experience
              the authentic charm that often goes unseen.
            </p>
            <a class="read-more" href="#">Read more</a>
          </article>

          <article class="post-card ">
            <div class="post-image image-2">
              <span class="pill">Lifestyle</span>
            </div>
            <div class="project-stack" aria-label="Project tech stack">
              <span>
                <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/typescript/typescript-original.svg" alt="TypeScript" />
                TypeScript
              </span>
              <span>
                <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/docker/docker-original.svg" alt="Docker" />
                Docker
              </span>
              <span>
                <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/postgresql/postgresql-original.svg" alt="PostgreSQL" />
                PostgreSQL
              </span>
            </div>
            <div class="post-meta">29 Jan 2024 • 5 mins read</div>
            <h3>A Fashionista's Guide to Wanderlust</h3>
            <p>
              Explore the intersection of fashion and travel as we delve into
              the wardrobes of globe-trotters.
            </p>
            <a class="read-more" href="#">Read more</a>
          </article>

          <article class="post-card ">
            <div class="post-image image-3">
              <span class="pill">Tips &amp; Hacks</span>
            </div>
            <div class="project-stack" aria-label="Project tech stack">
              <span>
                <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/python/python-original.svg" alt="Python" />
                Python
              </span>
              <span>
                <img class="icon-invert" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/flask/flask-original.svg" alt="Flask" />
                Flask
              </span>
              <span>
                <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/redis/redis-original.svg" alt="Redis" />
                Redis
              </span>
            </div>
            <div class="post-meta">26 Jan 2024 • 15 mins read</div>
            <h3>Top 5 Apps and Gadgets That Will Transform Your Journeys</h3>
            <p>
              Explore the latest in travel technology with our guide to must-have
              apps and gadgets.
            </p>
            <a class="read-more" href="#">Read more</a>
          </article>

          <article class="post-card">
            <div class="post-image image-4">
              <span class="pill">Culinary</span>
            </div>
            <div class="project-stack" aria-label="Project tech stack">
              <span>
                <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/laravel/laravel-original.svg" alt="Laravel" />
                Laravel
              </span>
              <span>
                <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/postgresql/postgresql-original.svg" alt="PostgreSQL" />
                PostgreSQL
              </span>
              <span>
                <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/docker/docker-original.svg" alt="Docker" />
                Docker
              </span>
            </div>
            <div class="post-meta">24 Jan 2024 • 10 mins read</div>
            <h3>Savoring Mosaic Resto Gastronomic Delights</h3>
            <p>
              From street food to fine dining, uncover the flavors that define a
              destination and the stories behind them.
            </p>
            <a class="read-more" href="#">Read more</a>
          </article>

          <article class="post-card">
            <div class="post-image image-5">
              <span class="pill">Destination</span>
            </div>
            <div class="project-stack" aria-label="Project tech stack">
              <span>
                <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/typescript/typescript-original.svg" alt="TypeScript" />
                TypeScript
              </span>
              <span>
                <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/go/go-original.svg" alt="Go" />
                Go
              </span>
              <span>
                <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/redis/redis-original.svg" alt="Redis" />
                Redis
              </span>
            </div>
            <div class="post-meta">20 Jan 2024 • 8 mins read</div>
            <h3>Journey Through Time</h3>
            <p>
              Wander through ancient streets, visit iconic landmarks, and immerse
              yourself in the tales that shaped them.
            </p>
            <a class="read-more" href="#">Read more</a>
          </article>

          <article class="post-card">
            <div class="post-image image-6">
              <span class="pill">Culinary</span>
            </div>
            <div class="project-stack" aria-label="Project tech stack">
              <span>
                <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/python/python-original.svg" alt="Python" />
                Python
              </span>
              <span>
                <img class="icon-invert" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/flask/flask-original.svg" alt="Flask" />
                Flask
              </span>
              <span>
                <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/docker/docker-original.svg" alt="Docker" />
                Docker
              </span>
            </div>
            <div class="post-meta">18 Jan 2024 • 6 mins read</div>
            <h3>Experiencing Sustainable Culinary Tourism</h3>
            <p>
              Discover how mindful dining can support local communities while
              offering memorable and delicious travel moments.
            </p>
            <a class="read-more" href="#">Read more</a>
          </article>
        </section>
      </main>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
